    <description>Maraviroc is a marketed drug for the treatment of HIV-infection. Maraviroc will be supplied in two different oral dose forms, 150mg and 300mg given twice a day. The drug will be dosed according to the recommendations in the product label i.e. with PI/r the dose is 150mg bid except, Maraviroc 300mg bid can be used at the discretion of the investigator if the PI/r is fosamprenavir/r; those randomised to the 2N(t)RTI arm, will receive Maraviroc 300mg bid. Patients randomised to receive Maraviroc will be provided with bottles of Maraviroc which contain a 30-day supply.</description>
